title: [FSX] TrueLandscape France 1.30 (FranceVFR)
description:
A new landclass to cover all France is named TRUELandscape, by FranceVFR. Like any landclass, it places the dense cities, little towns, industrial zones, forests and agricultural fields in the place they should be.

It uses the textures you have already installed (default, Ground Environment X, or other third party). It makes the landscape look good for every region where you donÃ¢â‚¬â„¢t have photoreal textures, instead of the default and repetitive FSX grid.
